subject: Boats and Boating
Sailboats and Sailing
America's Cup
lead_paragraph: The America’s Cup champion Alinghi of Switzerland asked a New York court to disqualify the American syndicate BMW Oracle Racing as Challenger of Record if it does not provide details about its 90-foot trimaran within 30 days.
